{"tid":850833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（長文）一人一個返工柒到無眼睇嘅事","createTime":"2018-10-06T17:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T17:31:06.000Z","uid":214541,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"301773fdbe93de45790cfce9f6f4a8f5b21584cc","tid":850833,"uid":214541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，細路係一名Sales仔，咁平時返工同事之間都會用walkie作為對話用途，如果要去廁所或者食煙，通常都會放低個walkie嘅。<br />\n話說今日店長用緊個walkie戴埋耳機出左去食煙（平時同事都唔會戴），我又on99睇唔到佢隻耳仔多左舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁正路都以為佢無攞到個walkie出去，就打算用自己部手機播歌，因為佢平時都會播英文歌嘅，咁聽得多就會自自然然聽返中文歌，係我轉左歌嘅時候仲要懶係醒咁用walkie問啲同事，我啲歌係咪好聽過佢好多呢！仲要唱埋首歌出泥！誰不知店長一直都聽緊walkie，返到入泥嘅時候望住我冇講野。全場靜撚晒<br />\n過左一陣，佢就同我講<br />\n店長：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喂，轉歌啦，啲歌好難聽啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喔，好啊。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：啲歌咁難聽，一定係你播緊啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻意識到佢頭先係聽到我講野，我當時柒撚到無地自容，成班同事笑撚到仆曬地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放工走個時店長仲要用一個意味深長嘅笑容望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我係咪夠鐘辭職啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同事勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3112a738c794ab3287c3d5c8ed6a32cdd94cb651","tid":850833,"uid":214541,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"屌諗住放工去買個m記食，忘記我今日發生過嘅事，點知買完外賣行行下成個汽水袋爛撚左，成個餐最重要嘅汽水無撚左，就等於食豆腐火腩飯，無左豆腐，仲點稱得上做男人嘅浪漫啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁我仲食泥做咩啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}